# MA3151 Deterministic CAS Tutoring Engine

A pure **SymPy**-powered, **Streamlit**-fronted tutoring tool for the MA3151
Matrices and Calculus syllabus.  Every solver is a deterministic rewrite system;
no neural models are involved.  Practice problems are procedurally generated so
that solutions always have clean integer or simple rational answers.

---

